alt: Image description: a sticker is put on a pole, with a residential housing area visible in frame. The sticker contains a person with makeup, tattoos, facial hair and a dress. It says “I feel better when I wear a dress” in Arabic, with a link to www.alkhat.org
Image description: A white wall with some leaves and bushes on the bottom before it, and some sticks growing up the wall. Red graffiti spells ΑΝΟΙΧΤΑ ΣΥΝΟΡΑ, greek for Open the Borders
